      "updated_at": "2016-05-23 20:38:40 UTC",
      "body": "Glad it worked out. The `scalafmt` task taps into the incremental compiler to avoid reformatting the whole project on every invocation. Since I've seen other people bump into similar problems as you, it might be worth considering adding a `scalafmtIncremental` that does what `scalafmt` currently does and let the `scalafmt` task reformat everything just like `scalafmtTest` does."
    },
